Usage: disconnectDanglingPort [-help] [-keepInout] [-keepInput] [-keepOutput]
                              [-partitionOnly]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-keepInout         # but keep inout dangling port connected (bool, optional)
-keepInput         # but keep input dangling port connected (bool, optional)
-keepOutput        # but keep output dangling port connected (bool, optional)
-partitionOnly     # disconnect dangling port in partition (bool, optional)